urce/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I think my record speaks to that,\\\" the 37-year-old Sydney university lecturer said.\", \"from\": 846, \"to\": 930, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 898, \"end\": 915, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Sydney\", \"score\": 0.9999895018814543, \"rank\": 1.0498215455937132e-05, \"text\": \"Sydney university\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Sydney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/University_of_Sydney\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn lost all three of her match-ups against rival dancers and her performance was parodied worldwide, including by late-night US television host Jimmy Fallon.\", \"from\": 932, \"to\": 1091, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 932, \"end\": 936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9539434314100645, \"rank\": 0.048229277028801386, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 1059, \"end\": 1061, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9980619904645524, \"rank\": 0.0018988758129460138, \"text\": \"US\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 1078, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Fallon\", \"score\": 0.9999897284424172, \"rank\": 1.0271663079899313e-05, \"text\": \"Jimmy Fallon\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Fallon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jimmy_Fallon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Commentators have questioned how she qualified for the Games, with some of her more fierce critics back home calling her a national embarrassment.\", \"from\": 1093, \"to\": 1239, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An online petition - which has since been removed - even demanded she issue a public apology.\", \"from\": 1241, \"to\": 1334, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In theinterview, Gunn said it was \\\"really sad\\\" to hear the negative reaction to her performance.\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1432, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1353, \"end\": 1357, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9539434314100645, \"rank\": 0.048229277028801386, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I am very sorry for the backlash that the community has experienced, but I can not control how people react.\\\"\", \"from\": 1434, \"to\": 1548, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She added it was \\\"wild\\\" when media chased her in Paris following her display.\", \"from\": 1550, \"to\": 1627, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1599, \"end\": 1604, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999969318196, \"rank\": 3.068355029869219e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But that really did put me in a state of panic,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1688, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Gunn had previously spoken out against the \\\"pretty devastating\\\" hatred unleashed after the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1690, \"to\": 1790, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1690, \"end\": 1694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9539434314100645, \"rank\": 0.048229277028801386, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I went out there and I had fun.\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1824, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I did take it very seriously.\", \"from\": 1825, \"to\": 1854, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I worked my butt off preparing for the Olympics and I gave my all,\\\" she said in an August video message.\", \"from\": 1855, \"to\": 1959, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"While many ridiculed her performance on social media, Gunn's moves won support from others, including her fellow Australian Olympians and Australia's prime minister.\", \"from\": 1961, \"to\": 2126, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2015, \"end\": 2019, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"score\": 0.9539434314100645, \"rank\": 0.048229277028801386, \"text\": \"Gunn\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Clan_Gunn\"}, {\"begin\": 2074, \"end\": 2084, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"score\": 0.9959118148714555, \"rank\": 0.00366298349765561, \"text\": \"Australian\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australians\"}, {\"begin\": 2099, \"end\": 2108, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"score\": 0.9182646332299569, \"rank\": 0.08219880619670682, \"text\": \"Australia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Australia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"By Garrin Lambley \\u00a9 Agence France-Presse  WIN R2 000: Take The South African's SASSA Survey  The South African is hiring!\", \"from\": 2128, \"to\": 2249, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2138, \"end\": 2145, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lambley_railway_station\", \"score\": 0.867428301376007, \"rank\": 0.15283255529304277, \"text\": \"Lambley\", \"types\": [\"Q719456\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lambley_railway_station\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lambley_railway_station\"}, {\"